Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.93,0:00:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵守契约的话 你们整个种族都能得到回报
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.59,0:00:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那艘宇宙船破坏了的话 就不用做更过分的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始进入超空间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.47,0:00:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾吉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.78,0:00:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们又抛下艾吉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.51,0:00:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要他一个人战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.99,0:00:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还算什么近卫骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.50,0:00:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们决定放弃保卫这颗在战斗中濒临死亡的行星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.13,0:00:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以全舰队的力量支援贵舰阿尔哥诺特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.86,0:00:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了协助你们完成任务而战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.99,0:00:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要找到正确的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.37,0:00:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.27,0:00:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾吉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.68,0:00:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.25,0:02:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战阵布置得怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.40,0:02:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.37,0:02:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前已完成了80％
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.36,0:02:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CORE（核心）的移动会耽误一点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.34,0:02:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫他们快点吧 战斗马上就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黑铁族吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让那艘船逃掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.82,0:03:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要破坏的船只又增加了一艘 梅希塔卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不允许你拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.38,0:03:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,320){\fscy230}闪  光  的  诺  多  斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认到有Full-hedron出现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs18}译注：hedron--白银族自主做成的隐形立方体。也称为"hedron之盾"或"hedron之壁"。\NFull-hedron--白银族自主做成的用于移动或临时居住的宇宙船。由大量的hedron构成。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.26,0:03:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是白银族
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.31,0:03:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pearl Core（珍珠核心）保持目前的坐标
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.31,0:03:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs18}译注：防御型卫星要塞珍珠核心（Pearl Core）——装备了无数的保护层生产器的卫星要塞。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby Core（红宝石核心）和Topaz Core（黄宝石核心）上前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs18}译注：攻击型卫星要塞红宝石核心（Ruby Core）和黄宝石核心（Topaz Core）\N——装配了大量的加速器，形成花瓣的形状。要塞上安置的多段发射配置连装\N重力收束粒子炮是通过重力镜片来把生成的粒子光束集束起来，再发射出去。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以Blue Core（蓝宝石核心）为中心 维持舰队的航行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs18}译注：母舰型攻击卫星蓝宝石核心（Blue Core）——特化了母舰机能的卫星要塞。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby Core（红宝石核心）移动到－24013
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Topaz Core（黄宝石核心）到达131154
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.18,0:04:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星系外围上检测到强烈的时空震
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量敌方势力正从超空间中出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚兹·亚卓特舰队牵制住了敌方主力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要死啊 妮尔宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神感应线路上有数据显示
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是公主殿下的指引
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解释出来 转送到航行地图上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.72,0:05:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推定航路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.99,0:05:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡尔基诺斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.92,0:05:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦 你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.22,0:05:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么可能会被打败
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.37,0:05:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤迪的内心在动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样战斗下去 卡尔基诺斯会……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是契约造成的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.01,0:06:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅希塔卡在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话 我想代他去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人能够违背
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契约规定的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人能够代你做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么黄金族要给我们留下契约
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.48,0:06:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支配我们的契约与战斗 能给宇宙带来什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.82,0:06:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡尔基诺斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我速战速决
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔哥诺特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在本舰后部、距离2389上全速航行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.07,0:06:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱离星之道 全速航行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那位公主的指引吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨大的能量正在高速接近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20秒以内到达本星域
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指示Pearl Core（珍珠核心）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在直线上展开Generator（发生器）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前线的状况是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.26,0:07:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正处于交战状态
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方势力正在缓慢增大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby Core（红宝石核心）的斜线上出现了新的物体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据检测到的数据 推测是诺多斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.43,0:08:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以显示到屏幕上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.96,0:08:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺多斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.52,0:08:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pearl Core（珍珠核心）赶不及
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把多拉里奥队集中到该区域
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的炮击都没产生效果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个诺多斯做了什么手脚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.39,0:08:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不攻击我们 也不让我们攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是沉默着穿过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:08:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小看我们 怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.38,0:09:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把Pearl Core（珍珠核心）的Generator（发生器）调到最大值
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和行星磁场同调 形成重力场
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.28,0:09:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那个怪物从防护罩中揪出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.18,0:09:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的光芒只是光学迷彩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法逃出重力网的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.02,0:09:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“收网”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.05,0:09:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.29,0:09:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同调完成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击溃他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.54,0:09:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 后方有大量蚁冢逼近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.08,0:09:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是远离主力部队的群体而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入迎击体势
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持前进路线
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:09:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在蚁冢的更后方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离67247上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检测到巨大的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.52,0:10:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是艾吉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计他最少也战斗了200个小时以上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾吉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.97,0:11:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.05,0:11:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡尔基诺斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.76,0:12:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的力量应该不止这种程度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那艘宇宙船不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.70,0:12:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺多斯周边产生了巨大的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.44,0:12:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来他进入了攻击体势
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物苏醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰散开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受损舰和补给舰汇集到Pearl Core（珍珠核心）周围
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Core（蓝宝石核心）放出所有Main Wurm（无人战斗机）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:12:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用全自动攻击把蚂蚁击溃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.88,0:13:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把火力的80％集中到诺多斯身上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.01,0:13:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的对准蚂蚁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量急速增大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已超过了Pearl Core（珍珠核心）的保护层极限
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.99,0:13:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准诺多斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.95,0:13:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准修正完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.51,0:13:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准误差0.01％
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回 回避
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.81,0:15:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.02,0:15:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行星希尔哥特上有巨大的能量反应
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁看到都会明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.42,0:15:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行星死亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.72,0:15:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Topaz Core（黄宝石核心）受重创
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,60％以上的舰艇无法联络
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby Core（红宝石核心）、Blue Core（蓝宝石核心）受损严重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收容多拉里奥队
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.27,0:15:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰队躲到卫星要塞后方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pearl Core（珍珠核心）呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然和敌方诺多斯同调中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离行星完全崩溃还有多少时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,200秒以内
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这之前维持重力场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰队以及Ruby Core（红宝石核心）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.43,0:16:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Core（蓝宝石核心）集中到诺多斯周边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在应该马上终止同调 解放那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再受一次重创的话 有可能会全灭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.94,0:16:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我们要放了他 令阿尔哥诺特被击沉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是为了什么受损
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那颗行星又是为了什么被毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和死去的司令官们一样无能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.91,0:16:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导致了这种惨状
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在舰艇无视命令、擅自离队也无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby Core（红宝石核心）在PointN3
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.48,0:16:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pearl Core（珍珠核心）在PointN83待机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.64,0:17:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Core以及各舰队移动到880333
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法联络的一部分舰艇跟随舰队移动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然没有一个人逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.39,0:17:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊 因为我们都敬爱阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此才会丢掉性命啊 一群笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.53,0:17:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡尔基诺斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何黄金族要把那名诺多斯交给黑铁族
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是为了把这个宇宙划分为两股势力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.53,0:18:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两股势力？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小规模的群体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的所有敌人都被亚兹·亚卓特舰队有效地牵制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧钢队全机归舰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来本舰将以第3宇宙速度离开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再度进入Active Warp
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.56,0:19:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全欧钢队归舰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了星之道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.82,0:19:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是公主……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我令到大家陷入了危机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.44,0:19:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到这一点 我就很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.25,0:19:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪安奈拉是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.34,0:19:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你切实履行了“爸爸们”所说的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.52,0:19:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说黄金族吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔库罗斯会为你们开路的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.91,0:19:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪安奈拉只管前进
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.63,0:19:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着迪安奈拉认准的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.47,0:19:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样我们就能再次相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾吉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.80,0:19:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把航路发送给亚兹·亚卓特舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果行星希尔哥特真的崩溃了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.92,0:20:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对失去了星之道的他们来说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.06,0:20:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这艘船能成为他们的路标
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.19,0:20:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有强大的敌人正在赶过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.22,0:20:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以最大功率展开保护层
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.63,0:20:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探测周边的时空震与重力震
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.10,0:20:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检测到重力震
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在本舰正上方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.71,0:20:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.46,0:20:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,资料对照
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.83,0:20:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Fu、Full-hedron
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.06,0:20:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是白银族吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.82,0:20:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.41,0:20:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑铁族 不会让你们逃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于要准备进行超空间跳跃 保护层的能量供应不足
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.07,0:20:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于展开了保护层 Active Warp的能力填充停止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.10,0:21:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们来得真是时候 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护层 超空间跳跃 应该放弃哪一边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.48,0:21:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请按照我指引的方向前进
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.46,0:21:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.93,0:21:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请退下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.59,0:21:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击停止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急解除保护层
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.12,0:21:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Active Warp
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才是……怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.64,0:22:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪安奈拉公主
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.67,0:22:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.52,0:22:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪安奈拉公主
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.69,0:22:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪安奈拉公主
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.26,0:22:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪安奈拉公主
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.73,0:22:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪安奈拉公主
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.95,0:23:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们抛下了艾吉一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.60,0:23:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此时行星迪依紧逼眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 Heroic Age
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.81,0:23:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第9话 归还
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.76,0:22:30.79,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)}ずっと前から君のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.85,0:22:36.31,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)}知っていたけどこんな気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.31,0:22:41.53,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)}芽生えるなんて思わなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.61,0:22:46.83,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)}まさか君に恋するなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.89,0:22:51.55,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)}何気ない帰り道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.03,0:22:57.50,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)}夜空の星を見上げながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.54,0:23:02.44,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)}わざと遠回りして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.88,0:23:09.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)}君の肩にもたれて歩く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.17,0:23:16.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)}二人でいれば　どんなことでも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.35,0:23:21.62,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)}乗り越えられそうと言う君の
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.70,0:23:26.87,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)}真っすぐな瞳を見つめて思う
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.93,0:23:32.94,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)}君を愛してる
